175
00:10:33,329 --> 00:10:36,439
Pejabat tinggi di sini bisa menolak mayoritas.

176
00:10:36,669 --> 00:10:38,409
Lantas aku akan merampas hak inspektur

177
00:10:38,539 --> 00:10:40,339
sebagai inspektur kepala.

178
00:10:44,980 --> 00:10:48,350
