00:54:12,699 --> 00:54:13,899
Pak Kepala Inspektur.

956
00:54:14,530 --> 00:54:15,699
Pak Kepala Sekretaris Kerajaan?

957
00:54:16,070 --> 00:54:18,600
Ada apa menemuiku selarut ini?

958
00:54:31,649 --> 00:54:35,550
